Focus Punch.Description:
The user focuses its mind before
launching a punch. This move fails
if the user is hit before it is used. (-3 Prio)

Mud Sport.Description:
The user covers itself with mud.
This weakens Electric-type moves
for five turns. (+1 Prio)

Water Sport.Description:
The user soaks itself with water.
This weakens Fire-type moves
for five turns. (+1 Prio)

Lucky Chant.Description:
The user chants an incantation toward
the sky, preventing opposing Pokémon
from landing critical hits. (+1 Prio)

Magma Storm.Description:
The target becomes trapped
within a maelstrom of fire that rages
for 2 to 3 turns. (Capture)

Powder.Description:
The user covers the everyone in a powder
that explodes and damages the a Pokémon
if a Fire-type move is used. (+1 Prio, Powder)
